{"title":"New Fezzari Solitude sub-1000g carbon hardtail ready for fast laps & big hucks","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/08/new-fezzari-solitude-sub-1000g-carbon-hardtail-ready-for-fast-laps-big-hucks/","date":1612807233000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Designed using their Monoform carbon fiber manufacturing process, the new Fezzari Solitude is a lightweight hardtail mountain bike that pairs with anything from a weight-weenie 100mm XC fork up to a 140mm, fat-stanchioned trail fork. All with the same sub-1,000g frame!</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-XC-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-XC-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-scaled.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x272/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Fezzari Solitude XC dropouts\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-XC-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-scaled.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x272/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-XC-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-scaled.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 2560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-XC-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-297x167.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-XC-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-800x450.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads