t strong and durable. But that’s not all that’s new…<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vwKWUxAqgKs?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><h3>Fezzari Solitude geometry updates</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"Fezzari Solitude geometry 2021\" width=\"1091\" height=\"509\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1091px) 100vw, 1091px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry.jpg 1091w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry-297x139.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry-800x373.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry-120x56.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-geometry-768x358.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.c