ardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-1536x1097.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-carbon-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-696x497.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-carbon-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-1068x763.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-carbon-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-588x420.jpg 588w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-carbon-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-3-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>Recommended fork travel ranges from 100mm to 140mm. The prior Solitude was designed around a 120mm fork, so that may be the sweet spot, but versatility is good, too.</p><p>It uses their CleanCatch cable routing to prevent the cables and hoses from slapping around inside the tubes.</p><p>Here’s their product manager, Tyler Cloward, explaining the new Solitude:</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/s6tKB43X9do?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-carbon-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-carbon-hardtail-mountain-bike-2021-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengi