ke-2021-build-options-768x201.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-build-options-696x182.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Fezzari-Solitude-hardtail-XC-bike-2021-build-options-1068x279.jpg 1068w\"></a></p><p>Complete bikes start at $2,499 for a SRAM GX/NX build with Rockshox Reba RL fork and WTB ST i25 wheels…but check the lead time and you’ll find that it’s 30-35 weeks out (which shouldn’t come as a surprise). The top end Eagle AXS with SID SL Ultimate has a more reasonable 8-10 week lead time, but it’ll set you back $7,499. Framesets are $1,999. They come in black (carbon) only, with S/M/L/XL frame sizes. Full build specs available on their website, and each bike includes their 23 point custom set up and Lifetime Warranty.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-leader-1\"></span></p><p><a href=\"http://fezzari.com/solitude\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fezzari.com</a></p></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d68afec6ff08e018eb33ed7af9a1a45b75656c15ac23de7b710d81acad20161f","category":"Cycling"}